# 5) README.md

Oluştur:

md
# ITENTER Enterprise Theme

Premium WordPress theme developed for:

ITENTER Information Technology

## Features

- OnePage Design
- Gutenberg Support
- WooCommerce Ready
- SEO Optimized
- Multilingual Ready
- Responsive Design
- Custom CMS

## Requirements

WordPress 6+

PHP 8+



